Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZMM\c&H2128C5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\fs75\pos(1110,156)}即将迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班级分开以后感觉挺寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但上学放学下课时间我们都在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  为了缩短我们之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上学放学的时候试试二人三脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个主意太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.97,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,,#2  给你的礼物 \Npresent for you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,see you…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
